    <item>
      <title>印度高温现在比降雨更能预测食品价格</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-29/india-s-heat-is-now-a-better-predictor-of-food-prices-than-rain</link>
      <description><![CDATA[汇丰控股有限公司表示，追踪气温上升趋势正成为预测印度食品通胀的更好方法，比经济学家通常依赖的降雨模式更准确。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-29/india-s-heat-is-now-a-better-predictor-of-food-prices-than-rain</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 29 Aug 2024 09:10:25 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>凉鞋需求强劲，Birkenstock 确认前景</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-29/birkenstock-affirms-outlook-amid-strong-demand-for-sandals</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Birkenstock Holding Plc 确认了其 2024 年财务目标，并报告了强劲的盈利增长，因为消费者抢购更多高端凉鞋和木屐。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-29/birkenstock-affirms-outlook-amid-strong-demand-for-sandals</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 29 Aug 2024 09:10:19 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
